casebody.data:
First Department,

March, 1945.

(March 2, 1945.) National Brokerage Corporation, On Behalf of Itself and All Others Similarly Situated, Appellant, v. Travelers Insurance Company, Respondent.

Judgment and order unanimously affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Cohn and Callahan, JJ. [See post, p. 691.]
